laboratory_examinations.findings: The majority of the images are degraded by motion artifact. Liver appears within normal limits. No focal liver lesion noted. There are a few small subcentimeter gallstones near the gallbladder neck. No choledochal stones or biliary dilation. Mild inflammatory changes surrounding the pancreatic head were noted, with no pancreatic duct dilation or focal lesions. Multiple bilateral renal cysts identified.
